data.description:
Expanded Palmera floor plan offering a 3rd Bedroom / spacious den, on an amazing lot backing up to the golf course is now available in the popular 55+ active adult luxury retirement community of PebbleCreek. Enjoy the very best of Arizona indoor-outdoor living on your extended covered patio with gorgeous unobstructed panoramic views along the 16th & 17th fairways, framed by painted Arizona skies at dawn and dusk.

Enjoy a spacious eat-in kitchen with new gas range/oven, built-in microwave, new stainless dishwasher, stainless refrigerator, reverse osmosis system, pantry, and breakfast bar that opens to your inviting great room.

The primary bedroom features an expanded bay window that looks out to the fairway - plus adjoining ensuite bathroom with skylight, dual sinks a walk-in shower, private toilet, and a spacious walk-in closet. A secondary bedroom, sizable den with built-ins that can also be used as a 3rd bedroom, guest bathroom, and a large laundry room (washer and dryer included) complete this highly desirable split floor plan.

The spotless extended length 2-car garage includes attached cabinets, garage sink, soft water system, and space for a golf cart.

PebbleCreek provides the ultimate active adult Arizona lifestyle with top-tier amenities: creative arts studio, a state-of-the-art fitness club, beautiful indoor & outdoor pools, championship golf, popular pickleball courts, outstanding restaurants, a clubhouse, easy access to the I-10 freeway, and close proximity to entertainment and fantastic shopping.  Welcome Home!
